skip `number`\
where:\
&#x20;   \- id`string`\
&#x20;   \- id\_in`array`\
&#x20;   \- space:`string`\
&#x20;   \- space\_in:`array`\
&#x20;   \- author:`string`\
&#x20;   \- author\_in:`array`\
&#x20;   \- network: `string`\
&#x20;   \- network\_in: `array`\
&#x20;   \- state: `array`\
orderBy `string`\
orderDirection `asc` or `desc`

