### Get a single vote <a href='#vote' id='vote'></a>

{% hint style='warning' %}
Choices are indexed 1-based. The first choice has index 1.
{% endhint %}

#### Arguments <a href='#arguments' id='arguments'></a>

id `string`‚Äå

#### Example

{% tabs %}
{% tab title='Request' %}
```graphql
